QuestData.Title: Satchel of Culexwood
QuestData.Description: This lost satchel is filled with wood given by the nearby Culex trees. Fluttercatch would surely appreciate its return.
QuestData.LogDescription: Return the Satchel of Culexwood to Fluttercatch in the Banks of Life.
QuestData.RewardText: A whole sackful?! Wonderful! I'll be sure to put this to good use.
